cooking /ˈkʊkɪŋ/

N-UNCOUNT Cooking is food which has been cooked. 饭菜 

例： The menu is based on classic French cooking. 这个菜单以传统法国菜为主。 

2. N-UNCOUNT Cooking is the activity of preparing food. 烹饪 

例： He did the cooking, cleaning, laundry, and home repairs. 他做饭、打扫卫生、洗衣服，还在家修修补补。 

3. ADJ Cooking ingredients or equipment are used in cookery. 用于烹饪的 [ADJ n] 

例： Finely slice the cooking apples. 把做菜用的苹果切成薄片。 

4.  →  see also cook

